  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>Staff can print receipts for tickets and invoices at any time from the <strong>Ticket View</strong> page.</p><p><strong>Note</strong>: Since RepairQ is cloud-based, you will need to set up your printer with your computer, first, in order to print from your browser.</p><h3 id=\"PrintingaTicketReceiptorInvoice-AdditionalResources\">Additional Resources</h3><ul><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1932361958/Print+Settings+-+Receipt+Template\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1932361958\" data-linked-resource-version=\"7\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Print Settings - Receipts</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1933377656/Print+Settings+-+Invoices\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1933377656\" data-linked-resource-version=\"6\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Print Settings - Invoices</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1933672639/Email+a+Receipt+to+a+Customer\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1933672639\" data-linked-resource-version=\"14\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Emailing a Receipt to a Customer</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1934229707/QZ+Integrated+Printing+-+Start+Here\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1934229707\" data-linked-resource-version=\"13\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Introduction to QZ Integrated Printing - Start Here!</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1937014903/Clearing+Your+Cache+in+Chrome+Browser\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1937014903\" data-linked-resource-version=\"4\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Clearing Your Cache in Chrome Browser</a></p></li></ul><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"680\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1933279550/Instructional%20-%200091cd.png?api=v2\"></span><h2 id=\"PrintingaTicketReceiptorInvoice-PrintingaReceiptorInvoicefromaTicket\">Printing a Receipt or Invoice from a Ticket</h2><p /><p>1. <a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1933541674/Searching+for+Tickets\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1933541674\" data-linked-resource-version=\"4\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Search for an existing ticket</a>, or create a new ticket and save it in a new status.</p><p /><p>2. When viewing the ticket, available Ticket Actions are along the top row of the ticket.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1933279550/Print%20Receipt%20or%20Invoice%201.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>3. To print, click either the <strong>Print Receipt button</strong> (printer icon) or the <strong>Print Invoice button</strong> (page icon). This will open a print dialog preview page where you can select the printer destination.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"340\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1933279550/Print%20Receipt%20or%20Invoice%202.png?api=v2\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1933279550/Print%20Receipt%20or%20Invoice%203.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><h2 id=\"PrintingaTicketReceiptorInvoice-IntegratedPrinting\">Integrated Printing</h2><p>If you have set up <a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1934229707/QZ+Integrated+Printing+-+Start+Here\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1934229707\" data-linked-resource-version=\"13\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Integrated Printing</a>, these icons will look slightly different. Clicking a Print icon will automatically send the job to the printer designated in your Print Config settings.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"340\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1933279550/Print%20Receipt%20or%20Invoice%204.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>If you click the dropdown next to the icon, you can choose from the list of printers configured in your Automated Printing settings or print with Browser Dialog.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"226\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1933279550/Print%20Receipt%20or%20Invoice%205.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p><strong>Note</strong>: The Browser Dialog page will open in a new window and allows you to select the destination, layout, and other settings.\u00a0</p><p /><p /><p>START 1.18.X</p>",
